ttps://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0004-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0004-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0004-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Jabra Elite 7 Pro<br /><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Jabra Elite 7 Active</p><p>今次 Jabra Elite 7 Pro 耳機把咪高風放到了較為側邊的位置，而表面按鈕的接觸面會較 Elite 75t 大小小，但在真無線耳機界別來說，仍然是屬於很細小的類別。在佩戴上耳之後，你不會覺得有一塊很大的東西突出來，令你的尊容看上去更加自然，不會像外星人或從耳朵突兩條烏冬出來那樣。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Jabra Elite 7 Pro</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Jabra Elite 7 Active</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0013-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0013-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0013-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0015-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0015-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0015-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0015-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0015-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Jabra Elite 7 Pro</p><p>而 Elite 7 Active 擁有接近相同大小的機身。它不像其他運動耳機有對翼彈出來，甚至用耳掛掛在耳仔上，耳機使用液態矽膠與 ShakeGrip 塗層，耳塞物料也更具吸附力。小編實試時覺得由於耳機已是讓耳機戴上耳後不容易跌出來。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067419" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0021-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067420" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0021-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0021-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0023.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067421" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0023-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0028-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0028-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0028-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>語音通話清晰度提升</h2><p>小編個人來說買耳機最想要靚聲，不過其實幾多 wire 民都話想買一對講電話時通話清晰的耳機。今次 Jabra Elite 7 Pro 就用了雙重「保險」，在設計上先有骨傳導感應器，再有 6 組收音咪高鋒，利用演算法務求把通話變得更為清晰。在小編的測試時，發現在風力較強的地方，Jabra Elite 7 Pro 收音也能隔除很多風聲，街上的嘈吵車聲也能降低，令通話更為清晰。</p><h2>主動降噪功能表現出色<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>對音質影響細</h2><p>Elite 7 Pro 內置有 ANC 主動式降噪功能，而且開啟 ANC 時耳機續航力可達 8 小時（廠方數字），連同充電盒，總共有 30 小時的音樂播放能力。雖然未必是業界最強橫續航力，已經是相當高水平。充電盒採長條型圓邊設計，但低部平穩，可平放在桌面上。它亦支援無線充電功能 Qi，有線充電則為 USB Type-C 規格。ANC 的效能方面，它能夠對很多長期發出低頻率的機械作出反應，例如巴士、汽車、地鐵引擎聲，又或者風扇的摩打聲，都能作出不錯的消噪。雖然降噪幅度並沒有其他著重降噪功能品牌如 Bose、Sony 那麼強橫，但在大部份情況下仍是相當夠用。</p><p>而 ANC 對於音質的影響，較好多同類型耳機都輕微，也不像好多耳機開啟降噪後會突然大幅加大了「重低音」效果。開啟 ANC 後，你會聽到聲音密閉感更重，你只會在很寧靜的地方才聽到開啟耳噪後對高、中頻清晰度有一點點影響，但如在街上你不會在意這方面的事情。況且在寧靜的地方，你可關閉其 ANC 功能，以得到更清晰的音樂。</p><h2>音質測試：沉實而有厚度的重低音，不影響中高頻表現</h2><p>一對小小的耳機卻得到下潛感非常十足的重低音，一直是 Jabra 耳機調音特色，也是幾令小編欣賞的地方。今次 Elite 7 Pro 的重低量同樣有份量而且有迴響，足夠感受到低頻的震撼力，而在著重重低音的同時，保持到流行曲人聲清晰。整體來說適合喜歡聽流行曲時重低音較果較大的朋友。如果你追求的是歌曲每個樂器的整體清晰度、定位，需要有強大的音場的話，就未必是 Elite 7 Pro 的絕對強項。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-768x1662.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-710x1536.png 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706-947x2048.png 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0706.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>Jabra Sound+ 手機應用程式中，可控制低中高頻的表現力，如果你認為低音太強的話，也可手動調節一下。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-768x1662.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-710x1536.png 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707-947x2048.png 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0707.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0705.png"><br /></a></p><p>通過 MOOV 收聽《I Want》(陳奕迅, Lang Lang, Renee Fleming) 24bit 48kHz 1791kbps FLAC 時，可聽到人聲突出，男聲女聲都同樣清晰而有力，中高頻清晰度相當好，不過尖聲會較為突出少少。耳機同時會給到你有下潛力的背景鼓聲，而這些鼓聲不會疊住人聲。背景的音場迴響仍在，表現出三頻清晰的特點。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-768x1662.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-710x1536.png 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703-947x2048.png 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0703.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>再收聽《Dear My Friend,》(姜濤) 24bit 44.1kHz 1569kbps FLAC 時，可感受到男聲的舌音會較為突出，不過音樂音場不錯，可感受到歌曲的廣闊度。同時間音樂所給的重低音沉實而有力，而不會影響到其他成份的清晰度，可見 Elite 7 Pro 用來聽流行曲是頗為合適。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-768x1662.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-710x1536.png 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704-947x2048.png 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_0704.png 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2>總結：多方面高水平表現，高質重低音之選</h2><p>Jabra Elite 7 Pro 在機身體積、ANC 音質／效能、續航力，以至低中高頻的清晰度，與重低音強度與下潛度的平衡上做得相當好，再加上通話增強的特色，用於智能手機、電腦上聽音樂、睇戲、玩遊戲也是非常不錯的選擇。而 7 Active 雖然沒有骨傳導感應器，但價格上可再平少少，又有 Pro 版的其他優點。唯一可惜的是兩款耳機都不支援 aptX 等頻寬較高的傳輸規格，iPhone 機主不會有任何得失，但 Android 手機用戶就可能會有點失望。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
